<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lmạ nsytk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - lmạ nsytk bsbb qsạwty lqytk btḥbny lmạ trktk bsbb ḍʿfy nʿmtk gẖmrtny

[V2]
 ʿạjz lsạny ʿn ạlwṣf lmḥbtk yạ sydy bʿd snyn mrt mn ạlbʿd lqytk qbltny

[V3]
 wlạ hmk ḥạlty kạnt ạyẗ lkn qbltny

[V4]
 1- ḥby ldẖạty wḍʿf ạymạny wqlby ạlqạsy mạmnʿsẖ ḥbk lyạ

[V5]
 ḍạʿt ḥyạty wktr twhạny fqdt ạḥsạsy wạnt ḥnyt ʿlyạ

[V6]
 sẖftny jạylk mkswr jyt fy ṭryqy bạlnwr wjryt ạkẖdtny fy ḥḍnk wgẖsltny mn ạlsẖrwr

[V7]
 2- trkt mkạny ktrt ạḥzạny ḍạʿt qdrạty fy mkạn ạnạ fyẗ gẖryb

[V8]
 qsyt ạyạmy wḍạʿ slạmy wfḍlt ạlạmy ạlmwjwdẗ fy ạlṭryq

[V9]
 ạṣbḥt ạnsạn ḥqyr ʿlyạ ryḥẗ ạlkẖnạzyr

[V10]
 mạ fḍltsẖ ạlạ ʿlyk gẖạly ḥty wạnạ ʿbd ḥqyr

[V11]
 3- ạnsạn blạ qlb sẖạʿr bạldẖnb wkl ḥyạty kẖsạrẗ

[V12]
 wbrgẖm ạlbʿd lqytny bḥb gẖyrt ạlqlb wmlyt ḥyạty sʿạdẗ

[V13]
 gẖyrt mṣyry ạlmḥtwm wsẖlt kl ạlhmwm

[V14]
 wfrḥt ạnt byạ lwḥdk nsytny kl ạlhmwm</lyrics>
